What build level are the VE/GEF/EMF, also what Eclipse level is this and what
JRE are you using?

It seems that PaletteCmp can not be resolved.  Can you see a valid 
org.eclipse.ve.cde\cde_palette.xmi  definition file?

Suddently realized i was executing eclipse under Java tiger (which i have
recently set my JAVA_HOME to point to): i tried to run "eclipse -vm", specifying
the path to my 1.4 javaw and that solved the issue.

I'm terribly sorry for having bothered you with this false-bug.
Beg your pardon,
